{"tid":1340494,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"台灣傳媒》白衣人在元朗西鐵站亂棍打記者、議員 今夜香港多人頭破血流","createTime":"2019-07-21T16:02:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-21T16:09:12.000Z","uid":35790,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"7eedf0dadfd0e8a7327574ecbec3eb3b3c58663f","tid":1340494,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T16:02:02.000Z","msg":"反送中》白衣人亂棍打記者、議員 今夜香港多人頭破血流<br />\n<br />\n2019-07-21 23:49<br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕香港「送中條例」修訂的風波未息，「民間人權陣線」（民陣）發起721遊行，晚間9時左右傳出有白衣人士在元朗車站附近聚集，埋伏、伏擊示威者，有人被白衫人持竹條鞭打，背部充滿鞭痕，議員、記者也被圍毆。<br />\n<br />\n根據港媒《TMHK》報導，香港元朗有大批人士身著象徵支持警察、香港特區政府及建制派的白衣，卻疑似是黑社會人士，不僅針對身穿黑衣的反送中抗議群眾動粗，還衝入地鐵車廂無差別攻擊。<br />\n<br />\n受害者之一蘇姓男子說，他在元朗站一帶發現大批白衣人聚集，只說了句「原來真的有白衫人」，就被一群白衣人追打1公里，直到小吃店老闆和《TMHK》記者到場後才罷手逃散，蘇男掀開衣服，背部都是傷痕。<br />\n<br />\n另外，<span style=\"color: red;\">在晚間11時左右，元朗站有多位民眾被毆打濺血，《立場新聞》記者和立法會議員林卓廷都被圍毆。另外，據現場消息，雖然已有市民報警，但無人接聽，元朗站未見任何警員，在地鐵站也找不到職員幫忙；<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">一直等到23時25分左右</span>，才有零星警察趕到。</span><br />\n&lt;自由時報&gt;"},{"pid":"794a70fbf25983d80aebe97f01503565c7e7ad01","tid":1340494,"uid":35790,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T16:02:51.000Z","msg":"即時蜚聲國際"},{"pid":"ecb274478158d50793b31a2c687936521335b246","tid":1340494,"uid":29167,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T16:03:07.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1338170/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1338170/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />返唔到屋企嘅手足入黎!! 有地方落腳!!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a234465851cf299b5991af8917889fb2976fd30","tid":1340494,"uid":52090,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T16:03:13.000Z","msg":"有傳言相關村落，未fact check<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1339421/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1339421/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">白衫打人，克警掉頭走，扮睇唔到</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://streamable.com/wlfoq\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstreamable.com%2Fwlfoq&d=PG0fnU9ECAVDedUX85NM%2FCK1%2BumEGLY4xtueqN3WuFY%3D&h=5a0f83b5\" target=\"_blank\">https://streamable.com/wlfoq</a><br />\n<br />\n立場有live<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rWWkXNs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrWWkXNs.jpg&h=8f1cd8bc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/QzLNCyW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQzLNCyW.png&h=71a1dcbc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://i1.wp.com/tmhk.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/IMAGE-2019-07-21-221828.jpg?resize=800%2C445&amp;ssl=1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fi1.wp.com%2Ftmhk.org%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F07%2FIMAGE-2019-07-21-221828.jpg%3Fresize%3D800%252C445%26ssl%3D1&h=d4eb3f32&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://i0.wp.com/tmhk.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/IMAGE-2019-07-21-221842.jpg?fit=1126%2C750&amp;ssl=1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Ftmhk.org%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F07%2FIMAGE-2019-07-21-221842.jpg%3Ffit%3D1126%252C750%26ssl%3D1&h=7d9cfe66&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/zLWMTa5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzLWMTa5.png&h=f0ad5fb6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/BUp6Taw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBUp6Taw.png&h=81a28b56&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"h